body: I can't believe I got paired with Mother Teresa.
Now you'll be a good saint and do it all yourself, right?
One, I'll be too busy staring at Justin.
Two, the more I do, the lower your grade.
I wish I was paired with Tyler.
You two nerds would ruin the curve!
We're going to meet in the lobby before the show, right?
There's no way I'd be seen in that piece of junk car of yours.
It's louder than a garbage truck and smells ten times worse!
My dad's going to fix it.
Just donate it to the demolition derby.
They'll put it out of its misery.
